rows.name:
Did friend need something? For questions about
Dodonga Caravan, just ask Koko.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041407_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Koko about the caravan's business.

rows.label: qev041407_MSG0002
rows.name:
Biggest product here is pollen orbs made from various
Noctilum plants.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041407_MSG0003
rows.name:
Pollen orbs are classic Nopon snack, and orbs from
Dodonga Caravan are tastiest of all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041407_MSG0008
rows.name:
Dodonga Caravan pull out every stop to make biggest,
bestest firework ever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041407_MSG0009
rows.name: ...And here is contract for friend. Bye-bye![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041407_MSG0011
rows.name:
Dodonga Caravan sends up firework so huge,
Elder Nan will leap out of funk![ST:wait ]
